TEMP (elu ikuku) bụ usoro nkè World Meteorological Organization (WMO) koodu alphanumerical eji akọ akụkọ ihe méré eme nke mpaghara elu nke ikuku nke ikuku nke balloons ihu igwe wepụtara site na elu (ma ọ bụ n'ala ma ọ bụ n"oké osimiri)
WMO na-ahọpụta koodu ọnụọgụ FM-35 màkà TEMPs elu na koodu ọnọdụ FM-36 màkà TEMP ndị dabeere na ụgbọ mmiri.
Na njikọ na-esote, ị nwere ike ịchọta usoro (Manual on Codes) peeji nke iri asatọ na ise.
